{
  "id": "adv_event_2511_01_05",
  "title": "フェス\nティバルの\n始まりだよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――海外ツアー追加公演、初日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.2333335398000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.4933335081
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.4333334127
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ開演の時間ね。いよいよ新曲の初披露だけど\n曲の制作者として、今の心境はどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4333334127,
      "endTime": 12.033333603400001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.2473471163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "それが自分でもよく分からないんだ。やけに鼓動が\n速くて、指先が冷たくて……こんなことは初めてだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2473471163,
      "endTime": 23.3490021227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5473459719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "緊張するのは、それだけ本気で取り組んだってことよ\n本気だから結果がどうなるか心配で不安になるんだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5473459719,
      "endTime": 32.1399313448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.3539448577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "緊張……そうか、僕は緊張していたのか……\n曲を作ってる時から、ずっと違和感があったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3539448577,
      "endTime": 45.1281851607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3206115244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "わくわくしてるのに、同時に不安で……\n気持ちは高揚してるのに、焦ってテンパって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3206115244,
      "endTime": 54.3868020533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてかと思ったけど、原因がやっと分かったよ\n新曲を任されて、僕はプレッシャーを感じていたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5872781911,
      "endTime": 65.3518816152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.5539448577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕のせいでリズノワを台無しにしちゃいけないって\nプレッシャーを感じて、ずっと緊張していたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5539448577,
      "endTime": 74.24922855669999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.4539448577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "葵の様子がおかしかったのはそのせいだったのね\n……でも、なんだか嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4539448577,
      "endTime": 81.09394501029999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.6999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "だって、台無しにしたくないって重圧を感じるくらい\n葵にとってリズノワは大事な存在だってことでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3079585233,
      "endTime": 89.0492965856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2633100985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "葵がそこまでリズノワを大切に思ってくれて嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2633100985,
      "endTime": 93.2197727679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4337862808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "心外だな。僕は昔からリズノワのことが好きだよ\nそんなの分かりきってることじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4337862808,
      "endTime": 100.5578905899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7671196142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったわね\n……ねえ、私が緊張をほぐしてあげましょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7671196142,
      "endTime": 106.81711961420001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12008.431412400001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12608.431412399994
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8799.547576899997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.0311331271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "こっちを向いて……ふふ……\n貴方のほっぺたは温かいわね。むぎゅむぎゅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0311331271,
      "endTime": 114.1558496951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.6666671911
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.369863208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "……思い出したよ\nリズノワの初のワンマンライブの時も\nこんな風に僕のほっぺたを掴んでむぎゅむぎゅしたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.369863208,
      "endTime": 126.0674366791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.269863208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "大真面目な顔でむぎゅむぎゅする莉央がおかしくて\nあの時、僕はリラックス出来たんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.269863208,
      "endTime": 132.7898629982,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17363.470618000007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、昔を思い出して肩の力が抜けたよ\nでも僕だけされるのは不公平じゃないかな。……えい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.0031965414,
      "endTime": 144.3813186804,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12563.473176900005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13530.139843499996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14663.473176899999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.3146479925
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.569867277
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ふぁっ！？\nちょ、ちょっと、どうして私の頬を掴んでるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.569867277,
      "endTime": 149.60297389020002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.8169874031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてって、むぎゅむぎゅするために決まってるだろ\nお返しだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8169874031,
      "endTime": 155.6640621979,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6033.333333400009
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7030.1357747
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7996.802441299991
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9130.135774699995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.8503207365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_05-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃっ、ちょ、むぎゅむぎゅしないで\nそんなことをするなら、私だって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8503207365,
